title: Arbor Snowboards :: Parallel Parking - Park City
description:
After purchasing a parking spot to parallel park their pickup in the Park City parking lot, the Arbor team paraded the passage up to Park City’s perfectly prepped park to prepare yet another episode of Parallel Parking, which we’ve now procured for your personal viewing pleasure.
